{"tid":2368314,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"普京稱俄羅斯新冠疫苗是全球最好疫苗","createTime":"2021-01-16T05:41:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T05:41:34.000Z","uid":177168,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"62f16620ebd65d4cd4a288a72501db869b534679","tid":2368314,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T05:41:34.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"small\">2021-01-14 HKT 00:21</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1570277_1_L_20210114002137.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1570277_1_L_20210114002137.jpg&h=177c6e25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">普京表示，俄羅斯的新冠疫苗是全球最好疫苗。（路透社）</code></pre><br />\n俄羅斯總統普京表示，俄羅斯的新型冠狀病毒疫苗是世界上最好的疫苗，任何其他同類的疫苗，都沒有顯示出如此高的保護率及安全性，但普京表示，有需要了解清楚，疫苗在面對多種突變情況下的效力問題，就此仍需要深入研究。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯的新冠疫苗「衛星-V」在去年8月註冊，這款疫苗屬於人類腺病毒載體疫苗，採用兩劑次接種程序，分開三星期接種。俄羅斯當局早前聲稱，疫苗的有效率為百分之91.4%，可以百分百預防新冠病毒重症感染。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570277-20210114.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570277-20210114.htm&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyP1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=1ec6175d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1570277-20210114.htm&h=27746ddf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1570277-20210114.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ttu7svH.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTtu7svH.gif&h=a18192e3&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}